## Tech Stack

- **CLI Framework:** Typer with rich output
- **Structure:** Command modules in src/commands/
- **Packaging:** pyproject.toml with console_scripts entry point

## Conventions

- Use typer.Typer() app with sub-command pattern
- Each command in its own module under src/commands/
- Use rich for formatted console output
- Use typer.Option and typer.Argument for CLI parameters
- Include --help text for all commands and options
